	   <tr><td colspan=2>What I say (Take this with a grain of salt, I'm only 34) is that we should focus on our offensive skills and resistances.  I, personally, would probably take a level each of all the resistances, maybe an extra one of magic.<br><br>For Archetype?  Combat Fury, definately, Healing Adept, and Fear Resistance.  Fear is evil.<br><br>Class skills?  Divine Stun, Improved LoH, 2hand Bash, Fearless, Holy Steed, but they're all cool.  *grin*<br><br>At least, this is what I get when I start having dreams about actually getting out of hell levels. *grin*<br>&nbsp;<br>Dalantia Dragonet<br>Rogue Defender of Love, 34th Rank<br>Fennin Ro<br>Kings of Brotherhood</td></tr>
